{"word":"Ramah","slug":"ramah","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Ramah</b> <a href=\"#/H7414\">H7414</a> <br/> 1. A city allotted to Benjamin:<br/> - General references<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=18&verse=25'>Jos 18:25</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=7&chapter=19&verse=13'>Jdg 19:13</a> <br/> - Attempted fortification of, by King Baasha; destruction of, by Asa<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=15&verse=22'>1Ki 15:22</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=16&verse=6'>2Ch 16:6</a> <br/> - People of, return from the Babylonian captivity<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=15&chapter=2&verse=26'>Ezr 2:26</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=7&verse=30'>Neh 7:30</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=11&verse=33'>Neh 11:33</a> <br/> - Jeremiah imprisoned in<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=40&verse=1'>Jer 40:1</a> <br/> - Prophecies concerning<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=10&verse=29'>Isa 10:29</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=31&verse=15'>Jer 31:15</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=28&chapter=5&verse=8'>Hos 5:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=2&verse=18'>Mat 2:18</a> <br/> - Called Rama<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=2&verse=18'>Mat 2:18</a> <br/> 2. A city of Asher<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=19&verse=29'>Jos 19:29</a><br/> 3. A city of Naphthali<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=19&verse=36'>Jos 19:36</a><br/> 4. Called Ramathaim-Zophim:<br/> - A city in Mount Ephraim<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=7&chapter=4&verse=5'>Jdg 4:5</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=1&verse=1'>1Sa 1:1</a> <br/> - Home of Elkanah<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=1&verse=1'>1Sa 1:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=1&verse=19'>1Sa 1:19</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=2&verse=11'>1Sa 2:11</a> <br/> - Home of Samuel<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=1&verse=20'>1Sa 1:20</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=7&verse=17'>1Sa 7:17</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=8&verse=4'>1Sa 8:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=15&verse=34'>1Sa 15:34</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=16&verse=13'>1Sa 16:13</a> <br/> - David flees to<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=19&verse=18'>1Sa 19:18</a> <br/> - Samuel dies and was buried in<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=25&verse=1'>1Sa 25:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=28&verse=3'>1Sa 28:3</a> <br/> 5. See <a href='S:Ramoth-Ramoth'>Ramoth-Ramoth</a>"}]}